title: S15 Ep54: Unsolved Mysteries: Berkshire's UFO w/Marcus Clarke
itunes:title: Unsolved Mysteries: Berkshire's UFO w/Marcus Clarke
description:
Darkness Radio revisits Unsolved Mysteries: Berkshire's UFO with guest Marcus Clarke

Unsolved Mysteries is BACK on Netflix and delving into more cold cases and strange sightings of unknown phenomena. Today Dave Schrader & Tim Dennis speak with director for the hit series, Marcus Clarke about one of the most incredible stories featured on the triumphant return, The Berkshires UFO Encounter. This is a fascinating and surreal experience that spans 1 night, many cities and counties and untold experiencers!

PLUS we look at Supernatural News and read YOUR email encounters with the Paranormal.
